Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.38,0:00:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoku Gosenzo San'e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2: Furnace
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying both of those girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They both lost their memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And both had fang marks on their necks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's highly unlikely that there are other\Nvampires like Beth at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.48,0:01:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's true, then as commissioner,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as a member of the Hiraga family,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.11,0:01:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn my back on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you want me to investigate this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.82,0:01:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have no solid proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incidents continue to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we mustn't draw attention to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good point, but if a westerner like me investigates,\Nwon't I draw attention to the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already set things in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Jennifer just threw herself at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a goodbye kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Goodbye"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sakura-san gave me a new assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pretty serious job,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm done taking care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going back to America?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Gen! One more please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Gen, I love you. Kiss me, my sweetheart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there are people watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'd cut it out if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's just an American custom. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looked like a big deal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you get one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.04,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So are you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she says, a kiss is just customary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, we've already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just said "Good morning" to Ayumi-chan,\Nbut she ignored me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had a handkerchief up to her\Nmouth, and her face was red, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make her cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit lightheaded again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt this way all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take you to the infirmary?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you kiss me, I might get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tease me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's no big deal. It's just a custom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that American woman your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lover? N-No, she's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're panicking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, just because we kissed doesn't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:06:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't mean anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.15,0:06:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you said, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.65,0:06:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though while we're on the subject, apparently you did\Nsomething even more impressive with Ayumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. If I breathe some outside air, I'll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What did you mean by...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm skipping first period. Tell me what I missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:08:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm done taking care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So she's really going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.53,0:08:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hear what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A female student from another class\Nwas found naked and unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.24,0:08:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes two of them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one two days ago was on the swim team,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the one yesterday was on the track and field team.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.62,0:08:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are saying it might be a child molester.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuck...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I was running a bit late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today on, I'll be your temporary English teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jennifer Collins. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:09:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skipping first period is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were sitting out here in this nice,\Nwarm sun, I'd be in the mood, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hold yourself back, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. You can relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.39,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making your body feel good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is my job as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... please kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If we confess our sins, He is faithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And just to forgive us our sins and\Npurify us from all unrightness."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Translated into Japanese,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Moshi watashi-tachi ga jibun no\Ntsumi o kokuhaku suru nara,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.16,0:10:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,kami wa shinjitsu ni tadashiku sono tsumi o yurushi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,subete no fui kara watashi-tachi o kiyome tamau."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.16,0:10:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this passage, do you see how the author is revealing\Nthe main character's struggle with evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei, don't–
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly. This is just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this? Does it feel good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Look how wet you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you lick it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.90,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go away soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, I went to the homes of\Nthe two girls who'd been assaulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:12:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But neither could recall anything\Nthat had happened to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, I left them with a purification serum.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.26,0:12:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Purification serum?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In layman's terms, it's a substance that\Nsuppresses vampire symptoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't defeat an actual vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it does help people who were\Nattacked by a vampire recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this vial with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only to protect Gen, but to protect\Neveryone at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you believe that the cause of this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The being that was left alive all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that it still serves a purpose\Nafter all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.52,0:12:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Oh"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really surprised me that Jennifer's\Nour new English teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't tell me anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to interrupt your lunchtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but can you show me around the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long. Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is her problem!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.32,0:13:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.20,0:13:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just directionally challenged, so I'm drawing a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this related to what happened yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Happened"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the girl from the swim team who was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear, were you looking at my butt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During class, you were staring\Nat my butt the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't! Everyone else was looking at it, but I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}First the swim team, then the track team.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if it's related to the rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's the girls' shower room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I need to go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.72,0:14:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. What kind of savage comes into\Na shower room with his clothes on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen! Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! More! More! Harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make your tongue stiffer. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you were staring at my butt.\NThis is what you wanted, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pretended you didn't care, but\Nyou really wanted me all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now I'm yours. Do what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mess me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More! Lick me harder! Lick me deeper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!! Gen! Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good! You're really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, can you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.29,0:16:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work it. Work it, Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work it harder! Yes. More of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck me, Gen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Fuck. Fuck me, Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck me. Oh! Yes! Fuck me. Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, fuck me! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.56,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cumming! I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it home by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine. I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you'd better have a doctor see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.72,0:16:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:16:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are. I was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.14,0:17:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you faint again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.77,0:17:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She said I should go home for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.98,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.57,0:17:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This belongs to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, thanks for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped working, so I threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.85,0:17:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, you can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a souvenir from your trip to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.56,0:17:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you did. You know, Gen was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember Gen saying he used to have the same pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:17:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These initials...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Gen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just cleaning up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be out here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi, I have something to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirakura Yoshino has left early due to dizziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.83,0:18:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, Itoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anyone know where Itoh Ayumi is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga-kun, do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Even I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of lunch period, I saw\Nher walking towards the pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with that new gaijin-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Jennifer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Class is finally over, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, Ayumi did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's not the type of girl to skip class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.30,0:19:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go look for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate it, Hiraga-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei! A girl is unconscious in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, let me through, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.95,0:20:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wasn't Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the students have gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the only one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I sent Mitsuko-sensei home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.52,0:20:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looked tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I didn't want to involve her\Ntoo deeply in this case anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.99,0:20:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I injected her with a purification\Nserum, and she's settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.49,0:20:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her parents should arrive shortly to take her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.50,0:20:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess it's all settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everything. Ayumi-san is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi is missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.52,0:21:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.81,0:21:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fear she's been attacked by some strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.73,0:21:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked her friends to call me if they found anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared. Stay here just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:21:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought it at a toy shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better have some weapons on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I injected the tips with that "purification serum" of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not stop the vampire, but it'll at least weaken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.74,0:22:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My top priority is protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go patrol the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.33,0:22:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.84,0:22:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If there really is a vampire out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.63,0:22:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then why did it target this school?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This feeling... It's exactly like the schools in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Ayumi comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.17,0:23:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll probably get mad and run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.26,0:23:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.39,0:23:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I understand, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That is fine. Do not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.20,0:23:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I will speak to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.25,0:23:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So our adversary is a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just doesn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.89,0:24:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiraga-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.31,0:24:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Ayumi will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.86,0:24:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose this will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'm going to school, I'll need to wear a uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it already left the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.37,0:25:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.21,0:25:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Someone's behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.97,0:25:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.52,0:25:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn vampire...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.20,0:25:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.37,0:25:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, you saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.46,0:25:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.33,0:25:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A naked girl. What's she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.97,0:25:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.05,0:26:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.51,0:26:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.61,0:27:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on Zoku Gosenzou San'e:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.03,0:27:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Possessed.
